{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"新民歌选","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":12,"day":3}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新民歌选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最近以来，不少文学刊物都发表了一些优秀的新民歌，这儿的十五首，就是其中的一部分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——编者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羌族新民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在高山望北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高路远不见城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羌民天天想念您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山隔人难隔心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《诗刊》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三重天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏族新民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔚蓝的天空有三重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一重出现了金色的太阳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是太阳啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是毛主席智慧的光芒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔚蓝的天空有三重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二重出现了银色的月亮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是月亮啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是各民族团结的征象。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔚蓝的天空有三重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第三重出现了灿烂的星光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是星光啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是藏族社员奔向社会主义的理想！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《四川文学》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月琴说话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彝族新民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月琴为什么会说话？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为琴弦会说话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琴弦为什么会说话？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为心儿会说话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心儿为什么会说话？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为奴隶变成凉山的主人啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《诗刊》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佤族新民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照到背阴坡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜到心窝窝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《人民文学》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上田有水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土家族新民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上田有水下田流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上田无水下无收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土家若无集体路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如锅里养泥鳅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《湖南文学》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王满夷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往日啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水涨了敲急锣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匪兵来了敲破锣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾难随着锣声到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家随着锣声破。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死的死了活的饿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣声没有一点乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣声诉的人民苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣声咒的世道恶！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲起锣声当战鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着红旗战山河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣声敲倒三座山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣声迎来新中国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲着锣鼓去报喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣声伴着花秧歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有党领导锣才响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮亮堂堂过生活！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《诗刊》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆苦思甜会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"居有松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉活了六十九，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从未上台开过口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天忆苦思甜会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似长江胸中流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千言万语说不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两滴热泪滑下喉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有一句不离口："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“跟党再活六十九！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《上海文学》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里滚滚人潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里扁担草帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里红旗招展，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里送粮小调。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《上海文学》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运棉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈官煊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩上担儿颤悠悠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扁担好像凤点头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬起头来望一眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里大路白银流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《延河》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何理山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是地基，山是篱笆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产队房子闪闪亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社篱笆开红花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山是牧场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山是粮仓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产队羊群像云飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的粮仓顶天上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山是摇篮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山是天梯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山家人人爱革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟党奔向社会主义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《河北文学》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺社有三宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺社有三宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长鞭铁锨宽刃镐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山要不走用鞭赶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地不开花用镐刨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三河六渠不听话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抡起铁锨疏河道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《河北文学》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村前流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张玉良"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村前流水长又长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员下地它照像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照下三百六十张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张张都有老队长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《诗刊》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队长见队长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山东新民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队长见队长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先把农活讲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比比谁干活多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕耩锄割在行不在行？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支书见支书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两手齐伸出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比比谁的茧子厚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想工作抓住没抓住？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《人民文学》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这间屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这间草房这间屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房里屋外不特殊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秫秸编花修篱笆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土皮麻墙爬山虎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒风腊月暖烘烘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燥热六月凉风出。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员爱屋因何故？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社成立在这屋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《鸭绿江》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新传说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱翠乔　马树国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻风刮，细雨下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社里肥堆天天大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁掏净老茅坑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不报工分不说话？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大爷卖粮丢了钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枉自提灯寻个遍；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半夜忽听门儿响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱从门缝往里钻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五好社员李铁旦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半身婆姨半身汉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋里没有烧火人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大忙谁帮作的饭？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺村好事多如星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记想问问不清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然满村起传说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人亲见是雷锋……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《火花》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}